<p>SIMple Gravity is one part of my SIMple Physics project. It is a simulator whose goal is to make learning and teaching universal gravitation more intuitive.
<ul>
    <li>Uses an immediate mode GUI framework</li>
    <li>In addition to real time graphics, outputs simulation data as a CSV file for further analysis</li>
    <li>Includes highly integrated Lua scripting for custom scenarios and interactions</li>
</ul>

